world, working to bring education about Bitcoin

7
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:04,820
and open blockchains to communities everywhere.

8
00:01:04,820 --> 00:01:10,460
His Patreon supporters make that work possible,
and they've made this event tonight possible

9
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:12,340
as well.

10
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:17,869
Most importantly, our next speaker is the
kind of person who would actually organise

11
00:01:17,869 --> 00:01:24,950
and host an event like this; one that benefits
